OL,5, A family was left "petrified" after the
OL,6, RAC failed to attend when their car    
OL,7, broke down at night, despite being on a
OL,8, disability priority list.              
OL,10,FSophie and Callum Smart were returning 
OL,11,Ffrom a birthday trip with their son    
OL,12,FKarson, who has cerebral palsy, when   
OL,13,Fthe car's clutch failed on the M1.     
OL,15,FThe family made many calls to the RAC  
OL,16,Fover seven hours but no-one turned up. 
OL,18,FThe RAC said: "We've apologised        
OL,19,Fpersonally to Mrs Smart for her and her
OL,20,Ffamily's experience."                  
